metatags.og:description:
35 likes, 1 comments - thorntonmartialarts on June 1, 2020: "TMA Fitness Challenge Day #1! 
Thorntons leading the way. 
Our Journal: We only did one run and it was before everything else. We didn't make a mile, running was the hardest part of the challenge for everyone but Kru. 
We need to work on our form on the push ups. It wasn't pretty but it is just the beginning. We did modify for the kids. They did 50 of everything and we will build them up from there. 
This is a challenge everyone can do. Always room for improvement. Keep trying, don’t quit. We all have to start somewhere and go from there. Join us on the journey!💥
.
.
.
#TMAFamily#TMAStrong#LetsGo#MuayThai#BJJ#MMA#TangSooDo#NoExcuse#Wetrain".
